{"tid":1863762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃之鋒：各國駐港領事向我收風評估「武肺」疫情","createTime":"2020-02-05T09:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T13:49:31.000Z","uid":5195,"like":578,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"b465ee25053323fe460a4f9ca29ecf42cd88570d","tid":1863762,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:37:10.000Z","msg":"【政府再唔封關 世界即將封港】<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎情況越加嚴峻，各地死亡個案有升幅趨勢，林鄭仍是堅拒封關，繼續中門大開，與民意背到而馳，方迫使醫護人員策動罷工。<br />\n<br />\n在罷工第三天，跟近百位議員前往政府總部，聲援醫管局員工陣線 HA Employees Alliance，聲討冥頑不靈的林鄭政府，也想跟大家說說國際層面的一點觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">這個多星期以來，不少國際記者和外國領事也聯絡我，詢問如何評估「武肺」一事對民情以及後續街頭抗爭的影響。</span>我的研判是，即使短期內因避免交叉感染而減少大型集會遊行，但政府在防疫工作上「口惠而實不至」，不分年齡階層地區均要排隊輪候求口罩，民怨在春夏之間再度爆發得比起去年六月更甚，也許只是時間的問題。<br />\n<br />\n外媒駐港特派員與各國駐港外交人員，職責所在當然要收集與分析本地民情，但我想令香港人值得憂慮的是 &mdash;&mdash; 現時政府繼續拒絕封關，一旦導致社區爆發傳染的話，屆時就只會是世界各地「封港」，<span style=\"color: red;\">均不見美國航空（AA）和聯合航空（UA）已宣布由本周六起停飛所有往返香港的航班。</span><br />\n<br />\n作為國際金融中心，各地與香港的商經合作互動相當頻繁，若果因為港府防疫工作表現不濟，導致航空公司相繼雪崩式地中斷所有航班，對香港經貿捐失的後果實在不堪設想。"},{"pid":"084848503cb982311ddde2edbe8e3125a2cb6f28","tid":1863762,"uid":271894,"like":180,"dislike":1,"score":179,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:38:17.000Z","msg":"屆時就只會是世界各地「封港」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPlease"},{"pid":"e58812858159f55a852086269b4927685543b1f9","tid":1863762,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7839e7b49099efcc8d0fe938562e4e263b5caf4","tid":1863762,"uid":346806,"like":64,"dislike":2,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:42:33.000Z","msg":"來吧<br />\n歡迎封港<br />\nWelcome <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2de3c693d5c060277c64d66274a7eaaf538df8","tid":1863762,"uid":218081,"like":16,"dislike":19,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:39:56.000Z","msg":"香港人!加油 <br />\n我接受 大家真係加油 運動最有希望既時候 多謝勇武手足<br />\n<br />\n香港人!反抗 <br />\n反條毛 見住勇武手足俾便衣拉 成堆人係度鳩叫放人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人!報仇 <br />\n我係黑警聽到你班廢柴咁嗌真係怪唔到佢地笑鳩我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人!抵死! <br />\n即管負評我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但呢個真係最符合香港現實情況既口號<br />\n<br />\n（警世）認清事實：醫護不可能無限期罷工<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1862120\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1862120</a><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n呢個垃圾post超過3000正評?<br />\n大家可唔可以運用下你個腦諗下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.discoverhongkong.com/common/images/about-hktb/pdf/tourism_stat_12_2019.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.discoverhongkong.com%2Fcommon%2Fimages%2Fabout-hktb%2Fpdf%2Ftourism_stat_12_2019.pdf&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=79a43275\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.discoverhongkong.com/common/images/about-hktb/pdf/tourism_stat_12_2019.pdf</a> 自己睇下12月內地訪港旅客人次<br />\n就算我當佢大部份只係香港機場轉機打個1折 都20萬<br />\n1月我再當佢打5折 都10萬<br />\n你唔駛識任何數學模型 唔駛識咩SIR Model 用下你常識諗 香港會唔會社區爆發?<br />\n係一撚定會啊你老母弱智閪 就算今日即刻封關都一撚定會啊<br />\n<br />\n所以我點解會出呢兩個post啊:<br />\n罷工既叫價一定要高<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/arndzeU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/arndzeU</a><br />\n<br />\n到今時今日 仲係大部份人唔識政治<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/arEsMfU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/arEsMfU</a><br />\n<br />\n大佬 雖然你地弱智 但我都唔想講咁白 而家我地係動用既整個社運既momentum同希望去爭取一樣近乎冇用既野<br />\n所以點解我會講叫價一開頭唔高搞到呢家唔上唔落<br />\n<br />\n仲有 醫護罷工本身已經係一樣唔道德既野<br />\n就算你既訴求係加薪定林鄭死全家 你都係唔道德<br />\n<br />\n點解你地既諗法唔係：「反正都俾人屌 倒不如去到最盡？」<br />\n係咪香港呢個奴性社會訓練到人既思維方式都有問題？<br />\n<br />\n罷工根本係all in or nothing 你係驚就唔好搞咁多野 你一係去盡all in 一係唔好搞<br />\n半桶水唔上唔落等俾人秋後算帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「社區爆發既話會返去救人」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eQacfS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eQacfS</a><br />\n唔好意思 今次唔係罷工 今次叫示弱<br />\n今次俾政府睇到我地既底線係超越唔到我地份垃圾工 那怕係會死<br />\n我寧願一開頭唔好搞<br />\n<br />\n[叫價]唔想俾人清算 就要反客為主<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ePNpvS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ePNpvS</a><br />\n你班友連「不被秋後算帳」呢個罷工最基礎條件都fight唔到就話死返去返工<br />\n我係醫管局高醫生都唔想理你啦 不過Mark曬你班廢柴既名準備以後清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知實會有柒頭衝出黎話 社區爆發咁所有Blame去曬林鄭到<br />\n哦...閱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁跟住呢?<br />\n仲有班傻鳩貼幾張facebook CAP圖話Connected 到藍絲<br />\n唉算 就當係? 咁跟住呢? 藍絲幫手叫釋放被捕手足?<br />\n我俾埋個劇本你啦:<br />\n社區爆發-&gt;死人-&gt;夏天到武肺開始收皮-&gt;民怨極點-&gt;FB IG暴動-&gt;HA清算醫護手足-&gt;Loop返半年前既野<br />\n冇錯 只會係咁 因為香港人!抵死!<br />\n<br />\nOK 實會有傻鳩衝出黎話 社區發爆唔醫人咁實好多人死<br />\n<br />\nAre you serious? 說好的攬炒? 死曬班廢老你呢個時候黎可憐?<br />\n冇攬炒既心態仲罷工? 香港人!等死!<br />\n唔敢去到最盡 咪等死 如果呢個係大家既選擇 咁唔好怨<br />\n<br />\n我5個月前開既post 到今日仲適用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭根本判斷100%正確 拉哂你班垃圾就得 因為你地惡唔出咩樣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aggKkiU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aggKkiU</a><br />\n<br />\n不過 我仍然要多謝醫護手足 你地冇智慧 但你地有勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地肯踏出第一步 比絕大部份香港人值得尊敬<br />\n至於其他行業既人<br />\n贈你地兩句:<br />\n條路自己揀 仆街唔好喊<br />\n可憐之人必有其可恨之處<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢到你仲睇得落 就睇埋呢兩個post啦<br />\n<br />\n醫護 特別係專職果班 罷工其實好難輸 唔好驚<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1860706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1860706</a><br />\n<br />\n有病人死左 我地bargaining power大左 五大訴求要升級<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eQhxAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eQhxAS</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人!抵死!"},{"pid":"89f756bcd47970148a890f75b4c32f86b931e82d","tid":1863762,"uid":51041,"like":97,"dislike":2,"score":95,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:41:59.000Z","msg":"之峰已成香港外交代表"},{"pid":"e223fb6903e61e3e9c8ded58af5527f1bd78ded0","tid":1863762,"uid":53026,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:42:12.000Z","msg":"有無可能九月選舉時民意逆轉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abcb027821bca6febe2787a806852616ceec584","tid":1863762,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef4a8a53362c667d9b20aa63e7d75e06887178d","tid":1863762,"uid":69447,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e223fb6903e61e3e9c8ded58af5527f1bd78ded0","tid":1863762,"uid":53026,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:42:12.000Z","msg":"有無可能九月選舉時民意逆轉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:57:55.000Z","msg":"愈來愈覺得林鄭準備辭職返英國<br />\n臨走前要盡忠+報復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n帶住所有罪名辭職 救選舉"},{"pid":"3c7e362a4270bf144215662ca870c77ec661b97a","tid":1863762,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59b9c8263f81b1683d7b68033668877dae6242c","tid":1863762,"uid":302917,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:59:12.000Z","msg":"加油之鋒，努力遊說各國封港please"},{"pid":"85e52c835fd66586edcefbb399caa2df63fc2220","tid":1863762,"uid":68080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:00:04.000Z","msg":"都知道會封香港啦唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6b8550d28c662a5b1b3824d454adb376fc5a40","tid":1863762,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b465ee25053323fe460a4f9ca29ecf42cd88570d","tid":1863762,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:37:10.000Z","msg":"【政府再唔封關 世界即將封港】<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎情況越加嚴峻，各地死亡個案有升幅趨勢，林鄭仍是堅拒封關，繼續中門大開，與民意背到而馳，方迫使醫護人員策動罷工。<br />\n<br />\n在罷工第三天，跟近百位議員前往政府總部，聲援醫管局員工陣線 HA Employees Alliance，聲討冥頑不靈的林鄭政府，也想跟大家說說國際層面的一點觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">這個多星期以來，不少國際記者和外國領事也聯絡我，詢問如何評估「武肺」一事對民情以及後續街頭抗爭的影響。</span>我的研判是，即使短期內因避免交叉感染而減少大型集會遊行，但政府在防疫工作上「口惠而實不至」，不分年齡階層地區均要排隊輪候求口罩，民怨在春夏之間再度爆發得比起去年六月更甚，也許只是時間的問題。<br />\n<br />\n外媒駐港特派員與各國駐港外交人員，職責所在當然要收集與分析本地民情，但我想令香港人值得憂慮的是 &mdash;&mdash; 現時政府繼續拒絕封關，一旦導致社區爆發傳染的話，屆時就只會是世界各地「封港」，<span style=\"color: red;\">均不見美國航空（AA）和聯合航空（UA）已宣布由本周六起停飛所有往返香港的航班。</span><br />\n<br />\n作為國際金融中心，各地與香港的商經合作互動相當頻繁，若果因為港府防疫工作表現不濟，導致航空公司相繼雪崩式地中斷所有航班，對香港經貿捐失的後果實在不堪設想。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDPGeQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDPGeQ.png&h=f227900c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家疫情有爆發跡象，十萬火急！藍田女手足全家確診武漢肺炎，請大家幫手簽下面的聯署：<br />\n<br />\n另外大家亦可以透過聯署同twitter自行遊說美方人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呼籲研發出肺炎解藥的美國藥廠供貨香港救手足救香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=2f0095f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n給予港府壓力封閉所有連接中國大陸的口岸<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/exert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fexert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=f4df5f13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/exert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國CDC、軍方醫療船派遣人員到香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpetition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=39299a32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter：<br />\nNCM Yue<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=5ea96b