3.000Z","msg":"芝鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外國已經認定芝鋒係外交人員"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:35:04.000Z","msg":"你地承認佢代表香港人？<br />\n<br />\n眾志 係建民主中國派wo"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:43:58.000Z","msg":"之前一路係主張自決喔，近排為明年選舉先del左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:52:49.000Z","msg":"咁前排係美國聽證會 <br />\n<br />\n講相信中國2047前會民主化係咩意思<br />\n<br />\n講明香港只要一國兩制 自治 不支持港獨wo<br />\n<br />\n佢代表香港人 即係承認香港人只想要中國比你嘅自治"},{"pid":"146cbb01e2d59cc0fa172ebc1918624c99f1ff1d","tid":1863762,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f90d4a57ab26dbda2ab9dc97e833b6ae715d0ef","tid":1863762,"uid":63936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:56:32.000Z","msg":"Gphone不如叫全世界封港算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b976c563deeb0ac899fb57bf136261ec362cccb","tid":1863762,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd6b8550d28c662a5b1b3824d454adb376fc5a40","tid":1863762,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b465ee25053323fe460a4f9ca29ecf42cd88570d","tid":1863762,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:37:10.000Z","msg":"【政府再唔封關 世界即將封港】<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎情況越加嚴峻，各地死亡個案有升幅趨勢，林鄭仍是堅拒封關，繼續中門大開，與民意背到而馳，方迫使醫護人員策動罷工。<br />\n<br />\n在罷工第三天，跟近百位議員前往政府總部，聲援醫管局員工陣線 HA Employees Alliance，聲討冥頑不靈的林鄭政府，也想跟大家說說國際層面的一點觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">這個多星期以來，不少國際記者和外國領事也聯絡我，詢問如何評估「武肺」一事對民情以及後續街頭抗爭的影響。</span>我的研判是，即使短期內因避免交叉感染而減少大型集會遊行，但政府在防疫工作上「口惠而實不至」，不分年齡階層地區均要排隊輪候求口罩，民怨在春夏之間再度爆發得比起去年六月更甚，也許只是時間的問題。<br />\n<br />\n外媒駐港特派員與各國駐港外交人員，職責所在當然要收集與分析本地民情，但我想令香港人值得憂慮的是 &mdash;&mdash; 現時政府繼續拒絕封關，一旦導致社區爆發傳染的話，屆時就只會是世界各地「封港」，<span style=\"color: red;\">均不見美國航空（AA）和聯合航空（UA）已宣布由本周六起停飛所有往返香港的航班。</span><br />\n<br />\n作為國際金融中心，各地與香港的商經合作互動相當頻繁，若果因為港府防疫工作表現不濟，導致航空公司相繼雪崩式地中斷所有航班，對香港經貿捐失的後果實在不堪設想。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDPGeQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDPGeQ.png&h=f227900c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家疫情有爆發跡象，十萬火急！藍田女手足全家確診武漢肺炎，請大家幫手簽下面的聯署：<br />\n<br />\n另外大家亦可以透過聯署同twitter自行遊說美方人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呼籲研發出肺炎解藥的美國藥廠供貨香港救手足救香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=2f0095f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n給予港府壓力封閉所有連接中國大陸的口岸<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/exert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fexert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=f4df5f13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/exert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國CDC、軍方醫療船派遣人員到香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpetition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=39299a32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/p